cs.LO, cs.FL, cs.LT, cs.DS, cs.PL

Reasoning: 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is the most likely category as the paper deals with the complexity of a logical problem, namely model-checking for freeze LTL on OCA. 
- cs.FL (Formal Languages and Automata Theory) is also a likely category as the paper involves automata and their reachability problem. 
- cs.LT (Theoretical Computer Science) is another possible category as the paper deals with the complexity of a theoretical problem. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is less likely but still possible as the paper involves algorithmic techniques for solving the model-checking problem. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is also less likely but possible as the paper deals with a formal language and its expressiveness.
